{"title":"organizational_diversity_domains_help","type":"markdown","params":{"fontSize":12,"markdown":"* This panel focuses on **Domains Diversity** in terms of **number of contributions and contributors**.
* **The big number** gives an overview of the active domains in the selected timepicker located at the top right section of the dashboard.
* **Pie Charts** show the distribution of the domains in terms of contributions and the number of people contributing.
* **Bar Chart** displays the number of active domains by data source over time for the selected timeframe of analysis.
* **Table** splits all of this information by data source and by domain. This gives the number of contributions and contributors.

[See complete panel documentation](https://chaoss.github.io/grimoirelab-sigils/panels/organizational-diversity-by-domains/)"},"aggs":[]}
